Search:   (AFFILORG("The Aerospace" PRE/1 Corp*) OR (AFFILORG(Aerospace PRE/1 Corp*) AND AFFILCITY("El Segundo" OR "Los Angeles"))) AND (PUBYEAR = 2018) AND ( EXCLUDE ( DOCTYPE,"ed" ) )  yields 188 results  
Need to include AFFILCITY "Los Angeles" search because several Aerospace Corp authors use PO Box in Los Angeles as affiliation address. 
Omitting Los Angeles would cause you to miss 29 results
